{"id":441656,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":27}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"150","ytitle":"","mtitle":"过去的历史","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬运工人的一条袴子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿了二十多年；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农的一件单衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披了四十个春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这衣袴磨破了几层皮?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这衣袴浸透过多少汗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细细的补呵!密密的缝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年盼明年，年年北风寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细细的补呵!密密的缝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针针行行是血泪凝住。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读熟这一本史册吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘记过去，就意味着背叛!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633r020601.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>贫农的一件单衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海工人文化宫举办“阶级教育展览会”展品</FONT>"}]}